{"tid":2441943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"膺電影評論學會最佳電影 籲港人守住腳步 《理大圍城》團隊：抗爭記憶唔會消亡","createTime":"2021-03-11T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T04:38:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e482bc2640041f7392c1fdc670311abf7447cd18","tid":2441943,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210311/IGL47TXS5ZCA7IQAEXBL24NBTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210311%2FIGL47TXS5ZCA7IQAEXBL24NBTM%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=889d9f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210311%2FIGL47TXS5ZCA7IQAEXBL24NBTM%2F&h=5aefc248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210311/IGL47TXS5ZCA7IQAEXBL24NBTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n膺電影評論學會最佳電影 籲港人守住腳步<br />\n《理大圍城》團隊：抗爭記憶唔會消亡<br />\n<br />\n疫情下，戲院被迫關閉逾百日至上月中重開，UA全線戲院周一更突然結業，蕭若元大嘆「香港電影已死」。香港電影評論學會大獎昨日才在這艱難時期舉行線上頒獎禮，反送中運動紀錄片《理大圍城》獲得最佳電影，電影團隊發表得獎感言提到：「屬於我哋抗爭嘅記憶、意志同掙扎，係唔會消亡。」並呼籲香港人要守住腳步，裂縫總有破開的一天。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：UA結業拖欠《鬼滅》拆賬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p8K4_xRrtC_CMUZjaDeWs5wjsNA=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOSPC5W6GZH7ZINNN3F2XXCDLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp8K4_xRrtC_CMUZjaDeWs5wjsNA%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNOSPC5W6GZH7ZINNN3F2XXCDLM.jpg&h=d1e5efa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【《理大圍城》】■《理大圍城》團隊得獎感言的片段，畫面中的隧道兩側，有「願榮」、「香港」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j3jdNv2R485IdTR4smB6NokCPkg=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KQPS2SQRJDEDLDGMI6OSEH6DI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj3jdNv2R485IdTR4smB6NokCPkg%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KQPS2SQRJDEDLDGMI6OSEH6DI.jpg&h=aa7c70d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■獲得香港電影評論學會大獎最佳電影的《理大圍城》，記錄前年11月中理工大學衝突事件。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8G88tWL3PobwAQ0C10DUN_muDl4=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/65AHMFZJLVE6NFPGVGXAWEPWT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8G88tWL3PobwAQ0C10DUN_muDl4%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F65AHMFZJLVE6NFPGVGXAWEPWT4.jpg&h=2eb0e8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《理大圍城》下周一於高先放映，昨早開售不足一小時，座位已全部轉為代表已售的紅色。<br />\n<br />\n自前年反送中運動揭幕，香港涉政治題材的電影接連受到打壓，儘管在風雨飄搖的日子，抗爭紀錄片《理大圍城》仍獲香港電影評論學會頒發最佳電影（詳見附表），實屬難得。香港電影評論學會大獎完整名單已在1月中公佈，頒獎禮原定昨日在西灣河電影資料館舉行，因疫情及頒獎場地休館改為錄播，得獎片段昨日在社交網播出。《理大圍城》的得獎感言短片背景是一條黑暗隧道，但盡頭終於見曙光，盡頭牆上寫有HK，而細心觀看隧道兩側，牆上有「願榮」、「香港」、「一不可」及「Five demands, not one less」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rAVKjYauduNNQwDuWY_hAgjfrEM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/REZRVIH2IRDE7K7HSCNT5LHJJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrAVKjYauduNNQwDuWY_hAgjfrEM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FREZRVIH2IRDE7K7HSCNT5LHJJY.jpg&h=a8547381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【《一秒拳王》】■《一秒拳王》男主角周國賢希望電影能為觀眾帶來更好的能量。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cg0mnzmgdQclFUp9YSIhyObJGow=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XSN3APFWIRBZNI5WVINEHKNBOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fcg0mnzmgdQclFUp9YSIhyObJGow%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXSN3APFWIRBZNI5WVINEHKNBOU.jpg&h=23bf2204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■執導《一秒拳王》的趙善恆盼望影迷能夠繼續支持香港電影。香港電影評論學會圖片"},{"pid":"5831340f7747913e10503e5a929c9e1b10c8078c","tid":2441943,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"投票成熟社會榜樣<br />\n<br />\n《理大圍城》得獎團體「香港紀錄片工作者」透過短片說︰「多謝電影評論學會喺今日咁艱難環境頒呢個獎畀我哋，一年過去，圍城並沒有消失，街上字句被抹走，點起嘅煙火亦被撲滅，但屬於我哋抗爭嘅記憶、意志同掙扎，係唔會消亡。」。。。。。<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n今日上映的《一秒拳王》入選推薦電影，導演及主演的趙善恆在得獎感言表示創作《一》片時，其實是想帶出一個重要訊息：「𠵱家世界好似好紛亂，係之前一秒一秒咁累積而來，將來會變成點，都係要靠我哋𠵱家一秒一秒去改寫。」趙善。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一部推薦電影《3cm》記錄香港罕見疾病患者生活，導演黃肇邦稱今年是他拍紀錄片的第10年，感謝電影評論學會外，又大讚獎項投票機制成熟，是現今社會的榜樣：「我好欣賞學會繼續堅持自己嘅方法，沿用自己嘅制度，就係透過對話同投票機制選出每一年嘅得獎作品，好多時有好。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯主演的《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》成為推薦電影外，亦獲得最佳編劇，導演梁銘佳則與太太Kate Reilly領獎，Kate說：「感謝丈夫與我一起訴說香港故事。」梁銘佳則說：「世道艱難，希望同業及香港人加油。」憑《奪冠》獲最佳導演的陳可辛，表示上次已是18年前的《三更》，他又代獲得最佳女演員的鞏俐多謝大家投票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Coy7VJb2X2Pql72x4p8-rXkEUg=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F5QVYXSAZRFH7AWRERMZ5LXGCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Coy7VJb2X2Pql72x4p8-rXkEUg%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF5QVYXSAZRFH7AWRERMZ5LXGCM.jpg&h=7f790305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》】■Kate Reilly除了有份撰寫劇本，亦與王宗堯主演戲中其中一個故事《鴛鴦》。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IzIjHnqSve_M4oDNyZawdgEUfdI=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LIKR4CCJZZG63OHR2A7CRHLKUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIzIjHnqSve_M4oDNyZawdgEUfdI%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLIKR4CCJZZG63OHR2A7CRHLKUE.jpg&h=c0ee8152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁銘佳與太太Kate Reilly奪得最佳編劇，兩人指是在非常有限的資源下完成作品。香港電影評論學會圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n8jj-MRnbRvf3n0qKsf1WlhoetQ=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YHANGN5IEJCDBLZKMXJVK4O7M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn8jj-MRnbRvf3n0qKsf1WlhoetQ%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYHANGN5IEJCDBLZKMXJVK4O7M4.jpg&h=29edd38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【《奪冠》】■鞏俐（左）在《奪冠》飾演中國女排教練郎平，獲得最佳女演員。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NcIaUw1jeaFEs_ioWQ8I98baG7M=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4PX76QTK6JD6JNH5D2HS4XCX7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNcIaUw1jeaFEs_ioWQ8I98baG7M%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4PX76QTK6JD6JNH5D2HS4XCX7U.jpg&h=7e6b9ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳可辛相隔18年再獲電影評論學會獎項，會長卓男親自頒獎。香港電影評論學會圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C_QEwrygULV4rrIblM5NmYnaYuo=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z6UCTB2HY5E2ROTD2BV5NOINFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC_QEwrygULV4rrIblM5NmYnaYuo%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ6UCTB2HY5E2ROTD2BV5NOINFE.jpg&h=7a31eb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【《3cm》】■《3cm》導演黃肇邦表示雖然每次大會公佈結果後有不同意見，但認為這正是投票機制成熟的結果。香港電影評論學會圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wXxxE5WEoJKLiKFs_hJQYiZ-5oY=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B3WI447A5RCCZJDP5DPYVUGTCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwXxxE5WEoJKLiKFs_hJQYiZ-5oY%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB3WI447A5RCCZJDP5DPYVUGTCA.jpg&h=d553b2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾麗芬開設的高先電影院成為首間播放《理大圍城》的商業戲院。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高先加場明日開售<br />\n<br />\n另外，高先電影宣前日佈於下周一至周日舉行「香港電影評論學會大獎&mdash;&mdash;得獎電影巡禮」，《理大圍城》於下周一晚上8時放映，門票昨早10時開賣，未夠一小時已經售罄，網民紛紛留言要求加場。高先昨日傍晚宣佈，在本月21日加開一場，門票於明日早上開售；由於昨日反應太熱烈，令購票系統故障，高先同時宣佈不設網上售票，當日要到戲院親自購票，每人限售兩張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N2ZLP_YdOvyPrG-FqP5WXK2dwIM=/753x391/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2UASVCEAABC6FIEC3JTQVQM4BE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN2ZLP_YdOvyPrG-FqP5WXK2dwIM%3D%2F753x391%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2UASVCEAABC6FIEC3JTQVQM4BE.gif&h=3ee111a5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}